* &quot;Manual of the Steam Engine and Other Prime Movers&quot; (1859)
* &quot;Manual of Civil Engineering&quot; (1861)
* &quot;Shipbuilding, theoretical and practical&quot; (1866)
* &quot;Manual of Machinery and Millwork&quot; (1869)

;Papers
